OL,7,FChelsea and Fifa have both launched
OL,8,Finvestigations after midfielder Enzo
OL,9,FFernandez apologised for posting a
OL,10,Fvideo which his teammate Wesley Fofana
OL,11,Fdescribed as "uninhibited racism".
OL,13,FThe French Football Federation said on
OL,14,FTuesday it would file a legal
OL,15,Fcomplaint over "racially offensive and
OL,16,Fdiscriminatory remarks" that were made
OL,17,Fby Argentina players on Fernandez's
OL,18,FInstagram livestream following their
OL,19,FCopa America final win over Colombia.
