OL,7,FThe footage appeared to show players
OL,8,Fparticipating in a chant about the
OL,9,FFrench national team, which dates back
OL,10,Fto when Argentina beat France in a
OL,11,Fpenalty shoot-out in the 2022 World
OL,12,FCup final.
OL,14,FThe livestream was ended by Fernandez
OL,15,Fbefore the chant was finished.
OL,17,FFernandez put a statement on social
OL,18,Fmedia on Tuesday night, saying: "I
OL,19,Fwant to apologise sincerely for a
OL,20,Fvideo posted on my Instagram channel
OL,21,Fduring the national team celebrations.
