OL,7,F"The song includes highly offensive
OL,8,Flanguage and there is absolutely no
OL,9,Fexcuse for these words.
OL,11,F"I stand against discrimination in all
OL,12,Fforms and apologise for getting caught
OL,13,Fup in the euphoria of our Copa America
OL,14,Fcelebrations. That video, that moment,
OL,15,Fthose words, do not reflect my beliefs
OL,16,For my character. I am truly sorry."
OL,18,FFrench-Chelsea footballer Wesley
OL,19,FFofana reposted the video on his
OL,20,Fsocial media, writing "Football in
OL,21,F2024: uninhibited racism".
